ffects of these drugs and in whom toxicity symptoms may be easily overlooked.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/91448/', '', 'Viloxazine', 'Amoxapine, Viloxazine, Lidocaine, Tetracaine', 1767369485);
